---
description: Route Unity AI work through Unity AI Workflow Kit.
globs:
  - "**/*.cs"
  - "Assets/**/*.unity"
  - "Assets/**/*.prefab"
  - "Assets/**/*.asset"
alwaysApply: false
---

Use `Assets/unity-ai-workflow-kit/AGENTS.md` as the primary workflow entrypoint.

Select the smallest relevant set of agent, rule, and skill files for the task. Use runtime artifacts for non-trivial features, reviews, and validations.
